  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Business and vocational skills training and cooperative development</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project is proposing the strengthening the Cooperative Union in Zavkhan province, consisting of primary agricultural cooperatives forming membership of those secondary cooperatives. This is a relatively new approach for Mongolia and the CUs will need significant capacity building in terms of leadership, setting up internal structures and policies, information and financial management, and most importantly, business strategizing and marketing. The project will achieve this through a process of intensive training and extension work.</narrative>
  </description>
